I'm a regular here. Bartenders are so good at cocktails and they will even just create one for you on the fly if it's not too busy.

Surprisingly good place near the Fox Theatre - perfect for pre-concert meal. PG&E shut off the gas main on the street before we arrived,  so they had to offer us alternatives to some of the items we chose. Server seemed a little overwhelmed/absent-minded,  but we still made it in time for the concert. I would go again.

I thought the food was excellent. Great pasta. Great wood fired pizza that reminded me of Naples. Fresh. Great service. They use local resources and businesses. Good stuff. I'll definitely be back. Thank you.

Great contemporary Italian restaurant with a California flair downtown Oakland. Plenty of good vegetarian options from top to bottom on the menu. Good cocktails and wine menu. Service was friendly and helpful.
